        "title": "Suites Egypt: 340% Sales Growth with Virtual Showrooms",
        "summary": "Premium furniture retailer transformed their sales approach with immersive Matterport virtual showrooms, achieving record-breaking online growth.",
        "description": "## The Challenge\n\nSuites Egypt, a premium furniture retailer based in Cairo, faced a common challenge: customers wanted to see and experience furniture in person before making significant purchases. With showrooms limited to Cairo and Alexandria, they were missing customers across Egypt and the wider MENA region.\n\n## The Solution\n\nArabiq created comprehensive virtual showrooms of their three flagship locations using Matterport Pro3 technology. Each piece of furniture was tagged with interactive hotspots showing pricing, dimensions, materials, and direct add-to-cart functionality.\n\nWe integrated the virtual experience with their existing e-commerce platform, enabling seamless checkout without leaving the 3D environment.\n\n## The Results\n\nWithin six months of launching their virtual showrooms:\n\n- **340% increase** in online sales\n- **12,000+ virtual visitors** from 24 countries monthly\n- **45% reduction** in return rates (customers knew exactly what they were getting)\n- **60% of sales** now come from outside Cairo/Alexandria\n\n## Client Testimonial\n\n\"Arabiq transformed how we sell furniture. Customers from Saudi Arabia, UAE, and beyond can now walk through our showroom as if they were there in person. The results exceeded our expectations.\" — Mohamed El-Sayed, CEO, Suites Egypt",
